'''Daegu Samsung Lions Park''' is a multi-use stadium in [[Daegu]], [[South Korea]]. It is used mostly for [[baseball]] games and is the home stadium of [[Samsung Lions]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Na|first=Yuri|title=삼성, 새 구장 명칭 확정 '대구 삼성라이온즈 파크'|url=http://sports.news.naver.com/sports/index.nhn?category=baseball&ctg=news&mod=read&office_id=311&article_id=0000476458|work=sports.news.naver.com|publisher=Xports News|accessdate=27 May 2015|language=Korean}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3015987&cloc=joongangdaily%7Chome%7Cnewslist2|title=Legacy of Lions slugger Lee evident at new home stadium|date=10 March 2016|publisher=Korea JoongAng Daily|author=Lee Hyung-seok}}</ref>

