{{Infobox country at games | NOC = JPN | NOCname = [[Japanese Olympic Committee]] | oldcode = | year = 2009 | date = | games = East Asian Games | location = [[Hong Kong]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | officials = | gold = 62 | silver = 58 | bronze = 70 | rank = 2 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = }}
'''[[Japan]]''' competed in the '''[[2009 East Asian Games]]''' which were held in [[Hong Kong]], [[China]] from December 5, 2009 to December 13, 2009. Japan finished second on the medal table with 62 gold medals.<ref>[http://www.hongkongextras.com/_hong_kong_2009_east_asian_games.html 2009 East Asian Games - Hone Kong Extras] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828061130/http://www.hongkongextras.com/_hong_kong_2009_east_asian_games.html |date=2012-08-28 }}</ref>
