'''Lobatse Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Lobatse]], [[Botswana]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home stadium of [[Extension Gunners]]. The stadium holds 20,000 people. Currently there is a progressive construction of stadium in Lobatse which is expected to be done by end of this year.
