{{no footnotes|date=June 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date=August 2012}} {{infobox country at games | NOC = MLT | NOCname = [[Malta Olympic Committee]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 2000 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.nocmalta.org }} | location = [[Sydney]] | competitors = 7 | sports = 5 | flagbearer = [[Laurie Pace]] | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
'''[[Malta]]''' competed at the '''[[2000 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Sydney]], [[Australia]].
==Results by event==
===[[Athletics at the 2000 Summer Olympics|Athletics]]=== '''Men's 100 m''' * [[Mario Bonello]] :* Round 1 &mdash; 11.06 (→ did not advance, 85th place)
'''Women's 100 m''' * [[Suzanne Spiteri]] :* Round 1 &mdash; 12.57 (→ did not advance, 69th place)
===[[Sailing at the 2000 Summer Olympics|Sailing]]=== '''Open laser''' * [[Mario Aquilina]] *# Race 1 &mdash; (40) *# Race 2 &mdash; (41) *# Race 3 &mdash; 25 *# Race 4 &mdash; 33 *# Race 5 &mdash; 30 *# Race 6 &mdash; 35 *# Race 7 &mdash; 9 *# Race 8 &mdash; 35 *# Race 9 &mdash; 32 *# Race 10 &mdash; 36 *# Race 11 &mdash; 37 *# Final &mdash; 272 (→ 37th place)
===[[Swimming at the 2000 Summer Olympics|Swimming]]=== '''Men's 400m Individual Medley''' * [[John Tabone]] :*Preliminary Heat &mdash; 4:53.12 (→ did not advance)
'''Women's 100m Butterfly''' * [[Angela Galea]] :*Preliminary Heat &mdash; 1:07.88 (→ did not advance)
